{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"9":"Zakat (Kitab Al-Zakat)"},"section_detail":{"9":{"hadithnumber_first":1556,"hadithnumber_last":1700,"arabicnumber_first":1556,"arabicnumber_last":1700}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1687,"arabicnumber":1687,"text":"Rapporté par Abu Huraira رضي الله عنه : Le Messager d’Allah ﷺ a dit : « Quand une femme donne quelque chose des biens gagnés par son mari sans qu’il le lui ait demandé, elle a la moitié de sa récompense. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (5360) Sahih Muslim (1026)"}],"reference":{"book":9,"hadith":132}}]}